import React, { useState } from 'react'; const ClientPanel = () => { const [scoreData, setScoreData] = useState({ teamName: 'India', batsmen: [ { name: 'Yashasvi Jaiswal', runs: 56, balls: 118, fours: 9, sixes: 0, status: 'c Shadman Islam b Nahid Rana' }, { name: 'Rohit Sharma', runs: 6, balls: 19, fours: 1, sixes: 0, status: 'c Najmul Hossain Shanto b Hasan Mahmud' }, { name: 'Shubman Gill', runs: 0, balls: 8, fours: 1, sixes: 0, status: 'c Litton Das b Hasan Mahmud' }, // Add other batsmen ], bowlers: [ { name: 'Taskin Ahmed', overs: 21, maidens: 4, runsGiven: 55, wickets: 3, econ: 2.61, wd: 0, nb: 0 }, { name: 'Hasan Mahmud', overs: 22.2, maidens: 4, runsGiven: 83, wickets: 5, econ: 3.71, wd: 0, nb: 0 }, // Add other bowlers ], totalScore: 376, overs: 91.2, extras: { b: 18, lb: 7, nb: 4, w: 1 }, }); return (

{scoreData.teamName} 1st Innings

{/* Batting Scorecard */}

Batting

{scoreData.batsmen.map((batsman, index) => ( ))}
Batsman R B 4s 6s Status
{batsman.name} {batsman.runs} {batsman.balls} {batsman.fours} {batsman.sixes} {batsman.status}
{/* Bowling Scorecard */}

Bowling

{scoreData.bowlers.map((bowler, index) => ( ))}
Bowler O M R W Econ WD NB
{bowler.name} {bowler.overs} {bowler.maidens} {bowler.runsGiven} {bowler.wickets} {bowler.econ} {bowler.wd} {bowler.nb}
{/* Extras and Total */}

Extras: {`b ${scoreData.extras.b}, lb ${scoreData.extras.lb}, nb ${scoreData.extras.nb}, w ${scoreData.extras.w}`}

Total: {scoreData.totalScore} ({scoreData.overs} Ov)

); }; export default ClientPanel;
